  <scopecontent id="aspace_40054747ea05b510fa7b55dd7127ff29">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Sixty-three photographs of prize-winning bovines, taken by Adrien Tournachon at the 1856 Universal Agricultural Competition of Paris. Sixty are cattle from France, Hungary, Germany, and England; three are long-haired sheep from Hungary.</p>  </scopecontent>
